data.name: theJobExecutor
desc: Can start registered uno services on triggered events and handle there own configuration and there lifetime. Such events are simple strings which meaning doesn't matter for any real service implementation of this specification. But triggered events must be available inside the configuration and some Jobs or AsyncJobs must be registered for that.
Prior to LibreOffice 4.3, this singleton was only available as a (single-instance) JobExecutor service.
